{"categories":[],"tags":[],"gallery":[{"img":"cms-data\/gallery\/blog\/mindtickler\/people-hurt\/d6984e2f-59f9-42c9-bcd0-169cf48437bf.jpg","alt":"","date":1530139487,"featured":false,"exif":{"focalLength":"","aperture":"","exposureBias":"","shutterSpeed":"","iso":"","date":"","make":"","model":"","copyright":"","caption":"","title":"","width":500,"height":375},"link":"","filename":"d6984e2f-59f9-42c9-bcd0-169cf48437bf","thumb":{"th":"cms-data\/gallery\/blog\/mindtickler\/people-hurt\/d6984e2f-59f9-42c9-bcd0-169cf48437bf-th.jpg","sq":"cms-data\/gallery\/blog\/mindtickler\/people-hurt\/d6984e2f-59f9-42c9-bcd0-169cf48437bf-sq.jpg"}}],"genre":"default","draft":false,"featured":false,"author":"Judy Cohen, Irreverent Mind","title":"People Hurt","permalink":"people-hurt","timestamp":1452931200,"summary":"<p>People hurt. &nbsp;<\/p><p>But, not spiritual people. Truly awake people don\u2019t hurt or get triggered, right?<\/p>","words":270,"content":"<p>People hurt. &nbsp;<br><br>Yes, even spiritual people.<br><br>People are depressed, anxious and sure there\u2019s something wrong with them.<br><br>For spiritual seekers, suffering can be extra painful because everyone knows that hurting is unenlightened, reaction is bad, and desires are a no-no.<br><br>I mean, truly awake people don\u2019t hurt or get triggered, right?<br><br>Of course. Everyone knows that.<br><br>So when triggering or pain does happen, that just proves how broken and hopeless we are.<br><br>Because being triggered is not cool.<br><br>Reacting supposedly indicates just how far we have left to go; how unenlightened and un-evolved we still are.<br><br>But what if that reactionless, desireless, never-afraid perfect you-that-feels-love-and-bliss only- what if that you simply isn\u2019t possible?<br><br>What if you never get there because that particular there isn\u2019t anywhere?<br><br>We are human. Humans feel. Humans react. Humans want.<br><br>That\u2019s never going away.<br><br>We live lives and deal with terrorism and screaming kids and global warming and love that leaves and computers that go black without backup and speeding tickets and death and illness.<br><br>Life goes on. Reactions happen.<br><br>Where\u2019s the problem with that?<br><br>And what real thing needs any of that to be one iota different, fixed or worked out?<br><br>Imagine how it would feel to not have to fix yourself or the planet.<br><br>Imagine all that free time just for experiencing life, as it is.<br><br>Ah.<\/p>","extra":""}